channel.title: Run Server Working but a problem...?!
channel.description:
Ok i compiled got everything right but when i used runserver.bat it says: [code] Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "P OSX" at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(NumberFormatException. java:48) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Integer.java:447) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Integer.java:497) at WorldObject.loadObjects(WorldObject.java:65) at WorldObject.<init>(WorldObject.java:16) at server.main(server.java:27) Starting Last Scape Server on 0.0.0.0:5555
[/code] I kno that it is working but thats this? [code] Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "P OSX" at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(NumberFormatException. java:48) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Integer.java:447) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Integer.java:497) at WorldObject.loadObjects(WorldObject.java:65) at WorldObject.<init>(WorldObject.java:16) at server.main(server.java:27) [/code] Never happened before... Also when i log in it says logging in from blah w\e but than it logs me out and says player already logged in plz try again in 60 secs... And that has NEVER happened before
